        "焚萊平場，柞木翦棘。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "柞"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "古国名，柞国。",
      "examples": [
        "柞，柞卜邑。",
        "柞，国名。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "柞"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "山名，如“莱柞”，二山名。",
      "examples": [
        "辭以無山，與之萊柞。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "柞"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "用作量词，手指张开的距离。",
      "examples": [
        "一柞來銅錢。",
        "指张开大拇指和中指两端的距离为一柞。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "柞"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "part_of_speech": "verb",
      "meaning": "用作“酢”，以酒回敬主人。",
      "examples": [
